{"id": 629, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心xSeesaw】你觉得喝过哪种咖啡才算有见识？", "description": "装X时间到！（题图来自unearthedcomics.com）", "record_count": 1717, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703152309M6Uur5Wm3joKcEJg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-11T11:14:02Z", "options": [{"id": 24577, "content": "板蓝根", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147567}, {"id": 24586, "content": "出名的庄园种植的高品质咖啡，经历从果到豆，再厉害的咖啡师新鲜烘焙，在合适的时间磨好现做出的咖啡。手冲或者塞风壶煮。重点是不加糖不加奶，像品茶一样品咖啡。喝出什么花香，浆果味之类的，不能有酸味和苦味，只能有植物自身的微甜，类似茶的甘甜和回甘的感觉。这样够装13不？会不会被喷死？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301070}, {"id": 26123, "content": "竞标豆，少见的微批次，90+，COE榜单常客。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 93729}, {"id": 24333, "content": "板蓝根", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216986}, {"id": 24597, "content": "香草味鲸屎咖啡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 301875}, {"id": 27416, "content": "豆浆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311254}, {"id": 24350, "content": "重要的不是咖啡，而是档次", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 33102}, {"id": 28964, "content": "任何东西在乎他是否有名还有意思吗 自己喜欢就好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328214}, {"id": 25134, "content": "服务员，给我来杯82年的蓝山拿铁，别放糖，别放奶，有奶的喝不惯，还有，别放醋，每次喝咖啡有有点酸酸的，不习惯。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302634}, {"id": 25136, "content": "虽然什么都没喝过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306031}, {"id": 24382, "content": "塞纳河左岸的咖啡馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269468}, {"id": 24386, "content": "客人:“为什么我的卡布奇诺那么轻，我在其他地方喝的分量好重的，你们在偷工减料！”---来自前星巴克员工的经历", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75694}, {"id"